OL,3,CRobert F Kennedy Jr apologises for
OL,4,C'pain' caused by Super Bowl advert
OL,6,FRobert F. Kennedy Jr has apologised to
OL,7,Fhis family for any "pain caused" after
OL,8,Fan advert for his presidential bid was
OL,9,Faired during the Super Bowl over the
OL,10,Fweekend.
OL,12,FThe advert was an almost exact replica
OL,13,Fof one used by his late uncle, former
OL,14,Fpresident John F. Kennedy, in his
OL,15,Fsuccessful 1960 election campaign.
