OL,3,CRobert F Kennedy Jr apologises for
OL,4,C'pain' caused by Super Bowl advert
OL,6,FThe independent presidential
OL,7,Fcandidate, who comes from one of the
OL,8,Fmost influential political families in
OL,9,Fthe US but has garnered a reputation
OL,10,Ffor his anti-vaccine activism and far-
OL,11,Fright influences, denied any
OL,12,Finvolvement in the ad.
OL,14,F"I'm so sorry if the Super Bowl
OL,15,Fadvertisement caused anyone in my
OL,16,Ffamily pain," he wrote posted on the
OL,17,Fsocial media platform X, formerly
OL,18,Fknown as Twitter.
