OL,3,CRobert F Kennedy Jr apologises for
OL,4,C'pain' caused by Super Bowl advert
OL,6,F"The ad was created and aired by the
OL,7,FAmerican Values Super PAC without any
OL,8,Finvolvement or approval from my
OL,9,Fcampaign."
OL,11,FMr Kennedy in April 2023.
OL,13,FHis cousin, Bobby Shriver, posted that
OL,14,Fhis mother, JFK's sister Eunice
OL,15,FKennedy Shriver, would be "appalled by
OL,16,Fhis deadly health care views."
OL,18,FMr Shriver continued: "Respect for
OL,19,Fscience, vaccines, & health care
OL,20,Fequity were in her DNA."
