OL,3,CRobert F Kennedy Jr apologises for
OL,4,C'pain' caused by Super Bowl advert
OL,6,FMr Kennedy responded separately to his
OL,7,Fcousin: "Bobby. I'm so sorry if that
OL,8,Fadvertisement caused you pain. I send
OL,9,Fyou and your family my sincerest
OL,10,Fapologies. God bless you."
OL,12,FAside from his family name, Mr Kennedy
OL,13,Fwas best known as an environmental
OL,14,Flawyer who fought for causes such as
OL,15,Fclean water.
OL,17,FBut in the last two decades he has
OL,18,Fbecome a leading voice in the anti-
OL,19,Fvaccination movement.
